6. Interface and UX Summary
The current interface follows a clean dark-green wellness theme with soft gradients, premium cards, illustrations, graphs, and supportive conversational text. The design is intended to feel similar to a premium health tracking application while still remaining unique to Flora. Images and illustrations are used to improve engagement in sections like Diet, Lifestyle, Gut Balance, Home, and Profile.

Visual principles used in the current UI:
- Large rounded cards
- Soft green-accent color palette
- Clear typography hierarchy
- Clickable category blocks
- Friendly dialogue boxes below analysis content
- Graph-led summaries instead of dense text
- Image-led section art for better user engagement

